@theparanoyds sent us into a frenzy with their buzzing guitar licks, spectral vocals, and quick-witted sardonic humor 🔥🛸 Check out their Audiotree Live Single, “Freak Out,” - out NOW! 

An unshakeable bond that began in preschool, The Paranoyds’ tight-knit fellowship has catapulted them into the hearts of a dedicated fan base. During their Audiotree Live Session, The Paranoyds’ traverse new sonic landscapes, experimenting with vintage synthesizers, toying with multi-layered drum tracks, and putting scuzzy garage rock riffs into hyperdrive. 

Single Release ⛓ link in b!0 + stories⛓
↳ Full ATL Session Release | 03.09

If high-energy licks and scandalously subversive songwriting send you spinning Wile E. Coyote style, it’s time to give @theparanoyds Audiotree Live Session a listen! 

Within the Venn diagram of new wave and garage rock, The Paranoyds have found their bunker smack dab in the middle. A well oiled machine, The Paranoyds’ melodic edge, punchy drums, and energetic baselines take their sardonic songwriting to the next level. 

Full Session Release ⛓  in b!0 + stories
